 幫我通一通 結果開既藥同上次一樣 仲少左一隻<br />\n我就覺得奇怪 中醫唔係把到我身體咩情況架咩 仲問翻我轉頭既<br />\n又食左3劑 都係無黎到 但每次食完藥都會有谷M既感覺 但食完無黎 個感覺又無左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63793f4f687c0e547b32ecffdc8c5f6b4a5d46a","tid":540722,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:33:13.000Z","msg":"其實M痛可以點做<br />\n做d咩先可以舒緩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求絲打解答"},{"pid":"8c5a968d9f5cfc643ab71c8b02f61a897c874741","tid":540722,"uid":48311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b63793f4f687c0e547b32ecffdc8c5f6b4a5d46a","tid":540722,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:33:13.000Z","msg":"其實M痛可以點做<br />\n做d咩先可以舒緩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求絲打解答"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:34:38.000Z","msg":"我都係痛得好勁個種人黎 我會用暖水袋囉"},{"pid":"971d66e43c14b175d91dd88ac48ebdb2293b9be0","tid":540722,"uid":143789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"你係唔係經常好夜訓？食無定時？"},{"pid":"31590a9e7dbd4df7127b1ff1f1526d0fb8d05794","tid":540722,"uid":48311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"971d66e43c14b175d91dd88ac48ebdb2293b9be0","tid":540722,"uid":143789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:36:21.000Z","msg":"你係唔係經常好夜訓？食無定時？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:37:21.000Z","msg":"係呀 成日失眠 ！食野都係不定時  成日胃痛"},{"pid":"fda4345ea83fe220ba98a1d0a88339faac8a517f","tid":540722,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c5a968d9f5cfc643ab71c8b02f61a897c874741","tid":540722,"uid":48311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b63793f4f687c0e547b32ecffdc8c5f6b4a5d46a","tid":540722,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-25T18:33:13.000Z","msg":"其實M痛可以點做<br />\n做d咩先可以舒緩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\